            React UI Forge Test
          </h1>
          <p className="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-2">
            Next.js Static App for Selenium Testing
          </p>
          <p className="text-sm text-gray-500">
            Following CLAUDE.md LAW 2: Tests must run on example Next.js static app
          </p>
